data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch in Graniteville built in 2019 in the sweet price point of only $264,900!! Fresh interior paint throughout!! Open floorplan features LVT in common areas with spacious kitchen and dining room! Custom cabinetry, oil rubbed bronze fixtures and Whirlpool appliances. Flex room and split floor plan with a large master suite and large walk-in closet! Landscaped yard w/ Rainbird sprinkler system, Radiant barrier roofing for energy efficiency!! Solar Panels included with purchase for minimal to no power bill at all! (solar panels will be paid in full for new owners!!) Call to schedule your appointment before its gone!
